title: Frida Kahlo Youth T-Shirt
description:
Frida Kahlo bravely shared her deepest feelings and struggles through her unique self-portraits.  Her strength continues to inspire millions of growing women today.  She captured the essence of her independence and openness when she wrote “I am my own muse.”
  • 60% ring-spun cotton & 40% polyester for a soft feel
  • Tagless, because nobody likes itchy tags
  • Printed in Chicago
